r />\n<br />\n如果暈倒，而施襲者想補刀，<br />\n咁條片一定有較大回響<br />\n當然，好似上面咁講，<br />\n要有人製定補刀個下<br />\n因為暈左個位，會失去保護反應"},{"pid":"51fb5d4f3e3aea03550ba70d146834967537870a","tid":1305723,"uid":4875,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T03:12:49.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">勇武咪還，和理非咪拍片！兄弟爬山各自做，不指責！</span></span>"},{"pid":"8666ad5c92a2c01fc478471b6273a05cf1aca186","tid":1305723,"uid":251414,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"891e15f23a0fee4a24098363eae2cb1b7eb62c33","tid":1305723,"uid":522,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T02:39:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BKMofAK.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBKMofAK.gif&h=caf841ec&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T03:13:22.000Z","msg":"有人打你的右臉連左臉也給他打， 但應該係非基督徒做咗出嚟， 我自己作為基督徒覺得好羞恥"},{"pid":"b57bdf8fa2f1f6873168b660f20aa103e46616a3","tid":1305723,"uid":243691,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"8666ad5c92a2c01fc478471b6273a05cf1aca186","tid":1305723,"uid":251414,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"891e15f23a0fee4a24098363eae2cb1b7eb62c33","tid":1305723,"uid":522,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T02:39:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BKMofAK.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBKMofAK.gif&h=caf841ec&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T03:13:22.000Z","msg":"有人打你的右臉連左臉也給他打， 但應該係非基督徒做咗出嚟， 我自己作為基督徒覺得好羞恥"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T03:15:15.000Z","msg":"政治潔癖"},{"pid":"df3b61b9beb5a705f0810da3f5ccbc1f4c9b6764","tid":1305723,"uid":260181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T03:17:25.000Z","msg":"自決啦<br />\n還拖要有心理準備被告打鬥<br />\n唔還都要避開，唔好on99比人打"},{"pid":"42c8e3d3806945eb3f4bec3ace357e89efe458b2","tid":1305723,"uid":44646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b57bdf8fa2f1f6873168b660f20